cast.overview: The youngest son of an alcoholic former boxer returns home, where he's trained by his father for competition in a mixed martial arts tournament – a path that puts the fighter on a collision course with his estranged, older brother.
cast.title: Warrior

details.biography: Laura Chinn created and starred in POP TV’s comedy FLORIDA GIRLS. She wrote the memoir ACNE, published by Hachette books. She was previously a producer and writer on FOX’s THE MICK, and a writer on FOX’s GRANDFATHERED. As an actor, she has appeared in movies and TV shows such as Grey's Anatomy, My Name is Earl, Happy Endings, and Warrior.
details.name: Laura Chinn
